body:
#### PR description:

This pull request is made because we want to introduce a range in Energy, R and Z in the CloseByParticleGunProducer Workflow. Now in the configuration file the energy, R and Z ranges must be specified, while the ParticleGun will select a random Energy, R and Z in those ranges.
In addition, a working snippet is added in the Generators folder.

@felicepantaleo
@rovere
